## 2. Market Segmentation & Expansion Vectors

### 2.1 Beachhead → Bowling Pin Strategy

```
PHASE 1: BEACHHEAD (Year 1)
├── Spatial Communities (WorkAdventure power users)
├── Remote-First Startups (culture-obsessed)
└── Executive Coaches / Leadership Trainers

PHASE 2: ADJACENT PINS (Year 2-3)
├── Enterprise HR (Psychological Safety measurement)
├── Sales Enablement (Deal intelligence)
├── Customer Success (Churn prediction via sentiment)
└── Healthcare (Telehealth burnout detection)

PHASE 3: MARKET DOMINANCE (Year 4+)
├── Insurance (Risk assessment via voice biomarkers)
├── Legal (Deposition analysis, witness credibility)
├── Government (Diplomatic negotiation intelligence)
└── Education (Student engagement & comprehension)
```

### 2.2 Total Addressable Market (TAM) Evolution

| Segment | TAM | Our Angle |
|---------|-----|-----------|
| Conversation Intelligence | $15B by 2028 | Emotion layer on top |
| Employee Experience Platforms | $12B by 2027 | Psychological Safety Score |
| Telehealth | $460B by 2030 | Burnout/depression markers |
| Metaverse Enterprise | $50B by 2026 | Native presence protocol |
| **Combined Serviceable Market** | **$80B+** | **CII as horizontal layer** |

