## 4. The Signal Processing Pipeline (Deep Dive)

### 4.1 Pipeline Architecture

```
                    INGESTION TIER
                         │
    ┌────────────────────┼────────────────────┐
    │                    │                    │
    ▼                    ▼                    ▼
┌─────────┐      ┌─────────────┐      ┌─────────────┐
│ WebRTC  │      │  File Drop  │      │  Bot Relay  │
│ Stream  │      │  (S3/GCS)   │      │  (Zoom/MS)  │
└────┬────┘      └──────┬──────┘      └──────┬──────┘
     │                  │                    │
     └──────────────────┼────────────────────┘
                        ▼
              ┌─────────────────┐
              │  AUDIO ROUTER   │
              │  (Kafka/Pulsar) │
              └────────┬────────┘
                       │
         ┌─────────────┼─────────────┐
         │             │             │
         ▼             ▼             ▼
    ┌─────────┐  ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐
    │ CLEANSE │  │ PARALLEL │  │ PARALLEL │
    │ Worker  │  │ Worker 2 │  │ Worker N │
    └────┬────┘  └────┬─────┘  └────┬─────┘
         │            │             │
         └────────────┼─────────────┘
                      ▼
              ┌───────────────┐
              │ SIGNAL FUSION │
              │    ENGINE     │
              └───────┬───────┘
                      │
    ┌─────────────────┼─────────────────┐
    │                 │                 │
    ▼                 ▼                 ▼
┌─────────┐    ┌────────────┐    ┌──────────┐
│REALTIME │    │  BATCH     │    │  WEBHOOK │
│WebSocket│    │  Analytics │    │  Delivery│
└─────────┘    └────────────┘    └──────────┘
```

### 4.2 Processing Stages (Enhanced)

| Stage | Model Stack | Latency Target | Output |
|-------|-------------|----------------|--------|
| **Cleanse** | DeepFilterNet v3 | <50ms | Clean PCM + Noise Profile |
| **Diarize** | Pyannote 3.0 + Custom | <200ms | Speaker segments + embeddings |
| **Transcribe** | WhisperX Large-v3 | <500ms | Word-level transcript + confidence |
| **Prosodics** | Custom Wav2Vec2-SER | <100ms | 47 acoustic features per segment |
| **Semantics** | Fine-tuned Llama-3 70B | <2s | Intent, sentiment, topic, entities |
| **Synthesis** | Mixtral-8x22B MoE | <3s | Psychometric state + recommendations |
| **Predict** | Custom LSTM/Transformer | <100ms | Next-turn prediction, risk scores |

### 4.3 The 47 Acoustic Features (Prosodic Fingerprint)

```python
PROSODIC_FEATURES = {
    # Pitch (F0) Features
    "pitch_mean": "Average fundamental frequency (Hz)",
    "pitch_std": "Pitch variability",
    "pitch_range": "Max - Min pitch",
    "pitch_slope": "Rising/falling intonation trend",
    "pitch_jitter": "Cycle-to-cycle frequency variation",

    # Energy Features
    "energy_mean": "Average loudness (dB)",
    "energy_std": "Volume variability",
    "energy_range": "Dynamic range",
    "shimmer": "Cycle-to-cycle amplitude variation",

    # Temporal Features
    "speech_rate": "Syllables per second",
    "articulation_rate": "Speech rate excluding pauses",
    "pause_frequency": "Pauses per minute",
    "pause_duration_mean": "Average pause length",
    "pause_duration_max": "Longest pause",
    "response_latency": "Time to respond after prompt",

    # Voice Quality
    "harmonic_noise_ratio": "Voice clarity",
    "spectral_centroid": "Brightness of voice",
    "spectral_flux": "Rate of spectral change",
    "mfcc_1_to_13": "Mel-frequency cepstral coefficients",
    "formant_f1_f4": "Resonance frequencies",

    # Interaction Features
    "turn_duration": "Length of speaking turn",
    "overlap_ratio": "% of turn overlapping others",
    "interrupt_count": "Interruptions initiated",
    "interrupted_count": "Times interrupted by others",
    "floor_hold_success": "% of interruption attempts that succeeded"
}
```

