## 8. Security & Compliance

### 8.1 Compliance Certifications (Roadmap)

| Certification | Target Date | Scope |
|--------------|-------------|-------|
| SOC 2 Type I | Q2 2026 | All services |
| SOC 2 Type II | Q4 2026 | All services |
| GDPR | Launch | EU operations |
| HIPAA | Q3 2026 | Healthcare vertical |
| ISO 27001 | Q1 2027 | Global |
| FedRAMP Moderate | Q4 2027 | Government |

### 8.2 Privacy Architecture

```
PRIVACY-FIRST DATA FLOW
═══════════════════════

1. CONSENT LAYER
   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │  Explicit opt-in per feature:           │
   │  ├── Basic transcription (required)     │
   │  ├── Signal analysis (opt-in)           │
   │  ├── Voice fingerprinting (opt-in)      │
   │  └── Cross-session learning (opt-in)    │
   └─────────────────────────────────────────┘

2. DATA MINIMIZATION
   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │  Audio → Features → Discard Audio       │
   │  (Raw audio deleted after processing)   │
   │                                         │
   │  Retention policies:                    │
   │  ├── Audio: 24 hours (processing only)  │
   │  ├── Transcripts: User-controlled       │
   │  ├── Signals: Aggregated, anonymized    │
   │  └── Fingerprints: Encrypted, isolated  │
   └─────────────────────────────────────────┘

3. ENCRYPTION
   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │  In Transit: TLS 1.3                    │
   │  At Rest: AES-256-GCM                   │
   │  Voice Fingerprints: Envelope encryption│
   │  Key Management: AWS KMS / HashiCorp    │
   └─────────────────────────────────────────┘

4. EDGE COMPUTE OPTION
   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │  On-device processing available:        │
   │  ├── WebAssembly models in browser      │
   │  ├── iOS/Android on-device inference    │
   │  └── Edge appliance for enterprise      │
   │                                         │
   │  "Zero-knowledge" mode: Audio never     │
   │  leaves device, only signals transmitted│
   └─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### 8.3 Enterprise Access Controls

```yaml
# RBAC Model
roles:
  org_admin:
    - manage_users
    - manage_billing
    - configure_integrations
    - access_all_analytics
    - manage_data_retention

  team_admin:
    - manage_team_members
    - configure_team_settings
    - access_team_analytics

  analyst:
    - view_analytics
    - export_reports
    - create_dashboards

  member:
    - record_sessions
    - view_own_sessions
    - view_team_aggregate_only

  guest:
    - view_shared_sessions
    - no_recording_rights

# Attribute-based access (ABAC)
policies:
  - name: "HIPAA-compliant-access"
    conditions:
      - user.clearance >= "hipaa_trained"
      - resource.classification == "phi"
      - time.within_business_hours == true
    effect: "allow"
```

