## 10. Growth Engine

### 10.1 Flywheel Model

```
                    ┌─────────────────┐
                    │   MORE USERS    │
                    └────────┬────────┘
                             │
                             ▼
              ┌──────────────────────────┐
              │  Better Voice Baselines  │
              │  (Network Effect)        │
              └────────────┬─────────────┘
                           │
                           ▼
              ┌──────────────────────────┐
              │  More Accurate Signals   │
              │  (Product Improvement)   │
              └────────────┬─────────────┘
                           │
                           ▼
              ┌──────────────────────────┐
              │  Higher User Value       │
              │  (Retention + Expansion) │
              └────────────┬─────────────┘
                           │
                           ▼
              ┌──────────────────────────┐
              │  Organic + Viral Growth  │
              │  (Word of Mouth)         │
              └────────────┬─────────────┘
                           │
                           └──────────────┐
                                          │
                    ┌─────────────────┐   │
                    │   MORE USERS    │◄──┘
                    └─────────────────┘
```

### 10.2 Channel Strategy

```
CHANNEL MIX
═══════════

PRODUCT-LED GROWTH (60%)
├── Free tier with viral hooks
├── "Powered by Subtext" badge
├── Shareable Tension Timelines
├── Chrome extension distribution
└── Open-source community

PARTNERSHIPS (25%)
├── WorkAdventure (co-marketing)
├── Zoom App Marketplace
├── Microsoft Teams Store
├── Slack App Directory
└── OEM/White-label deals

ENTERPRISE SALES (15%)
├── Outbound for Fortune 500
├── Industry events (Dreamforce, etc.)
├── Analyst relations (Gartner, Forrester)
├── Customer advisory board
└── Executive dinners
```

### 10.3 Pricing Psychology

```
ANCHORING & VALUE FRAMING
═════════════════════════

PERSONAL: Free → $9/mo
├── Anchor: "Otter costs $16/mo for just transcription"
├── Value: "Add emotional intelligence for less"
└── Upgrade trigger: Hit 5hr limit

TEAMS: $29/seat/mo
├── Anchor: "Gong costs $100+/seat"
├── Value: "Get 80% of the insight at 30% of the cost"
├── Land: Start with one team
└── Expand: Usage-based triggers for more teams

ENTERPRISE: Custom ($50-150/seat)
├── Anchor: "Qualtrics EX costs $200k+/year"
├── Value: "Real-time culture data vs. annual surveys"
├── Land: HR pilot
└── Expand: Sales, Success, all-hands

ROI CALCULATOR
├── Sales: "Detect 1 at-risk deal = pays for itself"
├── HR: "Prevent 1 burnout departure = 100x ROI"
├── Success: "Predict 1 churn = 10x ROI"
```

