# PART VI: EXECUTION ROADMAP

## 11. Development Phases

### Phase 0: Foundation (Weeks 1-4)
```
DELIVERABLES:
├── Project scaffolding (Python/FastAPI)
├── CI/CD pipeline (GitHub Actions)
├── Development environment (Docker Compose)
├── Model evaluation framework
├── Initial Signal Atlas implementation
└── Proof-of-concept: Single file analysis

TECH STACK DECISIONS:
├── Backend: Python 3.11+ / FastAPI
├── ML Pipeline: Ray + MLflow
├── Database: PostgreSQL + TimescaleDB
├── Cache: Redis
├── Queue: Redis Streams (start), Kafka (scale)
├── Frontend: Next.js 14+ / React
└── Infra: Terraform + Kubernetes
```

### Phase 1: Black Box MVP (Weeks 5-12)
```
DELIVERABLES:
├── Web app: File upload + analysis
├── Core pipeline: Cleanse → Diarize → Transcribe → Analyze
├── Tension Timeline visualization
├── Basic signal detection (6 signals)
├── User authentication (Auth0/Clerk)
├── Usage tracking + billing foundation
└── Public launch: subtext.live

SUCCESS METRICS:
├── 1,000 files analyzed
├── <30s processing for 5min audio
├── 85%+ signal detection accuracy
└── NPS > 40
```

### Phase 2: Live Wire (Weeks 13-24)
```
DELIVERABLES:
├── Real-time WebRTC streaming
├── Live transcript + signal overlay
├── Browser extension (Chrome/Firefox)
├── Mobile apps (React Native)
├── API v1.0 (REST + WebSocket)
├── First integrations (Zoom, Slack)
├── Team features + dashboard
└── Paid tiers launch

SUCCESS METRICS:
├── 10,000 MAU
├── <500ms end-to-end latency
├── $50K ARR
├── 3 enterprise pilots
└── 20 API developers
```

### Phase 3: Social Layer (Weeks 25-40)
```
DELIVERABLES:
├── WorkAdventure integration (flagship)
├── Gather.town, Mozilla Hubs integrations
├── Voice fingerprinting (opt-in)
├── Cross-session insights
├── ESP protocol v1.0 release
├── Partner marketplace
├── Vertical solutions (Sales, HR)
└── SOC 2 Type I certification

SUCCESS METRICS:
├── 100,000 MAU
├── $500K ARR
├── 20 enterprise customers
├── 100+ API integrations
├── ESP adopted by 3+ platforms
└── Series A ready
```

### Phase 4: Scale & Defend (Weeks 41-52+)
```
DELIVERABLES:
├── Advanced ML models (custom training)
├── Predictive analytics (churn, risk)
├── On-premise / edge deployment
├── Healthcare vertical (HIPAA)
├── International expansion
├── SOC 2 Type II
├── Partner ecosystem maturity
└── Category leadership

SUCCESS METRICS:
├── 1M+ MAU
├── $5M ARR
├── 100 enterprise customers
├── Industry recognition (Gartner MQ)
└── Defensible moat established
```

