## B. Risk Register

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Accuracy below threshold | Medium | High | Continuous model training; human-in-loop |
| Privacy backlash | Medium | High | Privacy-first architecture; opt-in only |
| Competitor fast-follow | High | Medium | Speed to market; open standard moat |
| Enterprise sales cycle | High | Medium | PLG foundation; strong free tier |
| Model costs at scale | Medium | Medium | Edge compute; model optimization |
| Key person dependency | Medium | High | Documentation; team expansion |

